= Municipalities and local governence

In Turkey, the territories of the republic are divided among small municipalities which are firmly connected with the central government. Still, the municipalities are stil an integral part of Turkish politics and are useful for reaching out to demographics we normally aren't performing well through an example of our governence and services.

- @governence: Municipalities are responsible for many local tasks in which we can improve our performance and show to the people how a CHP government would look like.
- @politics: The municipalities not only allow us to offer a vision of our administration but also to perhaps improve our political standing through the usage of local resources.
- @easy_discard

