- @publictransport: Public transport is a crucial part of urban life and most cities are lacking.
- @libraries: City libraries can be built to support education and increase literature consumption.
- @halkekmek: Municipal bakeries, organized under the programme "Halk Ekmek" can produce affordable bread to combat inflation and support worker families.
